{"tid":48200,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"62歲梁振英獲63歲外交部長讚年輕有為愛國愛港","createTime":"2016-12-21T02:17:43.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-21T15:12:57.000Z","uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"985616f1fae6e808d8fe1e1d9a75fcf3d545711a","tid":48200,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T02:17:43.000Z","msg":"已宣佈不爭取連任的特首梁振英到北京進行任內最後一次述職，今早拜訪外交部，並與部長王毅會面。63歲的王毅讚揚現年62歲的梁振英年輕有為、愛國愛港，成為行政長官之後，雖然面對複雜的內外環境，仍堅定奉行一國兩制政策，為國家、為香港做了大量有益的工作，獻出自己的心血。<br />\n<br />\n王毅又指港澳辦和中聯辦都代表中央政府對梁振英充分肯定，而雖然外交部不主管香港事務，但仝人非常支持他，亦感謝他作出的貢獻。<br />\n<br />\n梁振英表示，感謝王毅部長及外交部一直的支持，令香港在多方面都有良好發展，香港作為中國的國際化城市，有廣泛密切的對外關係，香港在外貿的經濟活動，體現高度國際化，現時在科技及文化，亦開展對外關係發展，而過程當中也為國家發展作出應有貢獻。"},{"pid":"13222115391a563b1db4e7ac8405f18b3cfe90b9","tid":48200,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T02:19:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56073224&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20161221\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56073224%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20161221&d=Dm165pHbRYEt%2BfaYXMEeUksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=36935dcf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56073224%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20161221&h=4f21adf8\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56073224&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20161221</a>"},{"pid":"5ca1d96613eab4b4c7c70d227da7c72782ba1ad9","tid":48200,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T02:19:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2c557ddbc49e5b8fdc63e09cf6576e414c817b5","tid":48200,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T02:20:44.000Z","msg":"可能順手讚埋自己有心有力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/c